{"tid":1189751,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"香港而家買樓真難 以前香港人一夠18歲就買到樓","createTime":"2019-06-07T02:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T03:37:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"749b975f2ed8cd038bb4974a44b4d40265aef8c9","tid":1189751,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"本身一家四口住在油塘公務員宿舍的李太，今早陪同兒子遞交白表，希望抽中一人單位。李同學今年剛滿18歲，希望成為年輕業主，「年齡唔係一個問題。」李太坦言「𠵱家買樓難，加上居屋平，希望畀個仔有間樓。」<br />\n<br />\n未上大學，李生已有父母願意支付首期，被問及將如何負擔供樓費用，本身有兼職補習的他笑言「要諗吓先！」這位應屆考生也慨嘆：「有層樓喺手安心啲！」李太也指，「日後有生活費，可以搞掂自己，先再算！」"},{"pid":"b8fb316c8b724ec3b21a35e0642ad00280131a8c","tid":1189751,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"支持租樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f16ca60be8f27bbc6760115cf9e1752ca771451","tid":1189751,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RS9NWc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RS9NWc.gif&h=37263d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前人嘅努力唔會白費，今次會由香港人做到"},{"pid":"fe2b11ad17507c25a85c72940cabe4124d838dcd","tid":1189751,"uid":73592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8fb316c8b724ec3b21a35e0642ad00280131a8c","tid":1189751,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"支持租樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}